<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜从背包里拿出她的围裙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师让孩子们都带围裙来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜的围裙是紫色的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是韩国的秀晶阿姨送的礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>秀晶阿姨每年都来美国一次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“波比，你的围裙不错嘛。” 贾森嘲笑他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比穿着一个有花边的粉红色围裙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我姐姐的。” 波比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你穿的是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的旧睡衣。” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我上美术课也穿它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Buon giorno！” 雪莉老师大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她戴着厨师帽。“这是意大利语的 ‘你好’。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天我们要做我最喜欢的意大利食物——披萨！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，我们要做的是一种小披萨点心，叫做披萨面包圈！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我吃过面包圈。我吃过披萨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，我从来没有吃过披萨面包圈！” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92833</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，每个人可以从篮子里拿六个切成一半的面包圈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师对他们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！每个人可以拿六个？” 波比大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。下一步是什么呢，波比？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把披萨酱涂在面包圈上。” 波比念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜把酱涂在面包圈上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等，我还要。” 贾森想要拿尼娜手里的酱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的面包圈从盘子上滑了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140810</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 尼娜躲开了面包圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>啪！贾森的面包圈都掉在了地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！” 贾森抱怨，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在该怎么办呢，雪莉老师？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156751</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抱歉，每个人只有六个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>需要有人跟你分享。” 雪莉老师回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我愿意分享。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，波比。” 雪莉老师说，“你真棒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170861</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在在面包圈上撒碎芝士。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不要撒太多。” 尼娜大声念道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定很好吃。我最爱芝士了！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198980</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后选择一种配料。撒在芝士上。” 莉琪念道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我选培根。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我选橄榄。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看！我在做披萨派！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女生们转过身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比拿着两个面包圈往空中扔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他假装自己在做面团。贾森哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“男生们，不要玩儿食物。” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 波比不小心撞到贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的盘子飞到空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森跳起来接。但是太晚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“又少了六个披萨面包圈。” 雪莉老师叹了口气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。女生们， 把你们的披萨面包圈放到烤箱里吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有东西焦了！” 雪莉老师跑到烤箱前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的披萨面包圈！” 莉琪大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“芝士放多了。” 贾森说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>芝士从面包圈上流下来，烤焦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，这里还有六个好的披萨面包圈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师从烤箱里拿出尼娜的面包圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295948</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“够所有人吃。” 尼娜笑了，“大家快吃吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295948</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。尼娜太棒了！” 大家欢呼起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师摘下她的厨师帽，戴在尼娜头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307300</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想快点为秀晶阿姨也做一份披萨面包圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>